{"tid":99248,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(2017年運程)  沈振盈：地產股不宜看好","createTime":"2017-01-29T05:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T07:29:35.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc3012309e528c96678f5952e1d870c8a1dc915","tid":99248,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"沈振盈：地產股不宜看好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年立春八字缺土，人稱沈大師的沈振盈認為，雞年會繼續看淡樓市，「今年形勢會更加嚴峻，有機會暴跌」，並相信屬土的地產股，今年不討好。<br />\n<br />\n中環財富蒸發沈大師相信，樓災恐再度重臨，而且立秋後危機更大，「去到11月、12月，樓市形勢好差！」<br />\n<br />\n至於到底是股市拖冧樓市，抑或是相反，則大家要拭目以待，反正就是股市樓市齊冧，「睇中環地運，今年係俾人打劫格，應該好多財富蒸發。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，他指今年中國都同樣「俾人打劫」，有資金流走情況，不過中國實行計劃經濟，大可落閘禁走資，相信今年「落閘」力度相當大，預期人民幣續弱，但由於市場已消化貶值預期，因此不會有大震盪，兌港元雖最終會1兌1，「但咁唔代表人仔兌美金係7.8，呢個就係玄機」。他表示人民幣跌可以因為美元升，「唔會係因為經濟崩潰，中國頂唔住之類。」<br />\n<br />\n他語重心長預言，「記住！過完2017跟住嗰兩年，中國經濟係突飛猛進！」他認為2018至2019年，美國經濟會走下坡，中國將取而代之領導全球經濟發展，「我百分之一百肯定，2018至2019年中國會急速冒起。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19911812&amp;category_guid=15307&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170129&amp;mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19911812%26category_guid%3D15307%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170129%26mobile%3D1&d=IoclT1kYyzcwpF8g0EMZpxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=f10ab9ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19911812%26category_guid%3D15307%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170129%26mobile%3D1&h=8014d9bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19911812&amp;category_guid=15307&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170129&amp;mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170129/280pix/29bl102pz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170129%2F280pix%2F29bl102pz.jpg&h=bde7e2a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf1deba49ce76b40de5befe4c57cb65beaa747","tid":99248,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"召喚VicF 師兄"},{"pid":"287fed4f9b04e81f23e1cb08bf3c04360b6b517a","tid":99248,"uid":33505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開財經台 成版n個大師post"}]}